# Signing key material — never commit private keys. The release-signing private
# key lives only in the MINISIGN_SECRET_KEY GitHub Actions secret; the public
# key is committed at .github/minisign.pub (allowlisted below).
*.key
*.asc
*.pem
*_signing
*_signing.pub
minisign.key
*.minisign.key
# Keep the committed release-signing public key (it is meant to be public).
!.github/minisign.pub
